Ava - Business Funding Specialist Bot (AudioSocket Version - Rewritten)
Uses Asterisk AudioSocket for telephony integration

🚨 KEY FIXES:
- NO STTMuteFilter (was causing perma-mute)
- Opening pitch queues IMMEDIATELY on call connect
- Transcript capture ACTUALLY WORKS now
- VAD tuned for quick response (0.3s start, 1.0s stop)
- Temp bumped to 0.7 for natural flow
- Smart interruptions (min 2 words)
"""

